<p>In honor of International Women's Day, Teamwork Commerce continued its commitment to giving back through the Teamwork Cares initiative.</p>

<h2>A second donation to EmpowHERment</h2>
<p>On March 17, our team donated 10 bags of clothing, shoes, and accessories to EmpowHERment, a nonprofit dedicated to helping women achieve mental, emotional, and financial self-sufficiency.</p>
<p>This marks our second time supporting this incredible organization. During the drop-off, we had the opportunity to meet Ambee Stephens, whose passion and leadership continue to make a meaningful impact in the community.</p>

<h2>About EmpowHERment</h2>
<p>Founded in 2018, EmpowHERment provides free resources including mentorship, workshops, and entrepreneurship training to support women as they rebuild, grow, and thrive.</p>
<p>We're proud to support organizations that create real change and look forward to continuing our partnership with EmpowHERment.</p>
